alon.shevach


-Book.java:
this is the book class, it represents a book.
book has title, author, year of publication and different literary aspects.

-Patron.java:
this class represent a patron that has book intrests,
the patron has firstname lastname and book preferences.
also he has an EnjoymentThreshold.

- Library.java:
this class represents a library, which holds books.
each library has a maximum number of books it can hold and
a maximum number of patron that are registered to,
and also a maximum number of book each patron can borrow.
